tip.text: Comforting and affordable steamboat. No pork, mutton or beef served here & there's only tomyam & chicken soup available. The owner's cute son gets +1 point for eye candy material :D
Honestly felt that food here is just mediocre. Overall pricey and overrated. Pictures look better than the real thing.
